Pooja Sharma was born on April 23, 1993 at 1:40 PM in Surajgarh, Rajasthan. She stands at 5'5" tall with a fair complexion. She completed her B.Com from Aggarwal College and is currently pursuing her MBA from Amity University. Her family includes her grandfather Ghysa Ram Sharma, late grandmother Bhagwati Devi, father Babu Lal Sharma who works in service, and mother Manju Sharma who is a homemaker.
